The xcode snippet project is used for managing the snippets in xcode.

The default snippets are stored in the ~/Library/Developer/Xcode/UserData/CodeSnippets/

We can check out this git project and use a soft link to the target directory.

For example: 

cd current git project directory
mv ~/Library/Developer/Xcode/UserData/CodeSnippets/ ~/Library/Developer/Xcode/UserData/CodeSnippets.backup
ln -s CodeSnippets ~/Library/Developer/Xcode/UserData/CodeSnippets/
